<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

	<PropertyGroup>
		<Nullable>enable</Nullable>
		<IsPackable>true</IsPackable>
		<IsTrimmable>false</IsTrimmable>
		<OutputType>Library</OutputType>
		<Deterministic>true</Deterministic>
		<AllowUnsafeBlocks>true</AllowUnsafeBlocks>
		<DisableImplicitMicrosoftCSharpReference>true</DisableImplicitMicrosoftCSharpReference>

		<Description><![CDATA[
Nalix.Runtime provides the core packet processing and middleware infrastructure for the Nalix ecosystem. It includes the middleware pipeline orchestration, packet dispatching channels, and execution management needed to handle message-oriented traffic with high efficiency and low latency.

It serves as the foundation for building complex message-processing workflows, offering a modular and extensible architecture that decouples transport logic from application-level packet handling.
		]]></Description>

		<PackageReleaseNotes><![CDATA[
- Initial release of the Nalix core runtime infrastructure.
- Implemented high-performance MiddlewarePipeline for asynchronous packet processing and orchestration.
- Introduced PacketDispatchChannel for reliable, observable packet routing and execution management.
- Optimized PacketContext for low-allocation metadata and state propagation through pipelines.
- Added support for NetworkBufferMiddlewarePipeline to streamline low-level buffer manipulations.
- Refined PacketDispatchOptions with granular concurrency and synchronization controls.
		]]></PackageReleaseNotes>

	</PropertyGroup>

	<Import Project="..\Nalix.Build.props" />
	<Import Project="..\Package.Build.props" />

	<ItemGroup>
		<ProjectReference Include="..\Nalix.Common\Nalix.Common.csproj" />
		<ProjectReference Include="..\Nalix.Framework\Nalix.Framework.csproj" />
	</ItemGroup>
</Project>
